      <p>The value of independent advice is that it&rsquo;s honest. We&rsquo;re a Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm, so we have a clear preference for QuickBooks and we disclose it &mdash; but we earn nothing on which platform you choose, so there&rsquo;s no reason to push you toward a poor fit. On a short discovery call we map your size, industry, inventory, entities, support, and ecosystem, then recommend the platform and tier that fit &mdash; and if that&rsquo;s Xero, Wave, FreshBooks, Sage, or Zoho Books rather than QuickBooks, we&rsquo;ll say so plainly. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not affiliated with any of the platforms named here. We don&rsquo;t publish competitor pricing because it changes; confirm current rates with each vendor.</p>
